# Requires "Require review from Code Owners" in branch protection to take effect.
#
# Everything that can change WHAT gets built, gated, or signed needs a human
# review before it reaches main (a push to main publishes signed images).
# images/<distro>/<version>/env is deliberately NOT owned: the daily
# snapshot-bump PR only touches env files, so it can auto-merge unattended
# and security patches keep shipping within 24h.
#
# Replace @CHANGEME with the repo owner/team (same placeholder convention
# as Makefile / scripts/build.sh).

/.github/               @CHANGEME
/scripts/               @CHANGEME
/policies/              @CHANGEME
/tests/                 @CHANGEME
/Makefile               @CHANGEME
/images/common/         @CHANGEME
/images/**/Dockerfile   @CHANGEME
